title: Leah Bracknell - Yoga and You DVDRip x264 aac [MP4]
description:
Filmed on location in Ibiza, Leah takes you through a practice that is easy to follow yet challenging. The programme covers a warm-up, sitting and standing postures, breath control and relaxation and is divided into five sections: 1) Awakening, 2) Taking Control, 3) Inner Strength, 4) Finding Balance and 5) Tranquility. Yoga And You balances a physical workout whilst encompassing a positive frame of mind. Leah Bracknell has been practicing Hatha Yoga for almost four years and is studying for the teacher training diploma at the British School of Yoga. This programme has been devised by Leah and British Wheel of Yoga qualified teacher Janet Kaye.
